Frequently Asked Questions

NAD+ (Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide) is a vital coenzyme found in every cell of your body. It's essential for energy metabolism and DNA repair. As we age, NAD+ levels naturally decline by up to 65%, contributing to the aging process.

ChronoNAD+ provides the precursors your body needs to produce more NAD+. The addition of Resveratrol acts as an activator, enhancing the effectiveness of NAD+ and providing a powerful boost to your cellular health and energy levels.

While individual results may vary, many users report feeling increased energy levels and mental clarity within the first few weeks of consistent use. Long-term benefits related to cellular repair and healthy aging build over time.
